trans-unit.source: Represents a ribbon toolbar that is always visible in the window frame to provide access to common commands.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett menyfliksområdet verktygsfält som visas alltid i fönsterram att ge åtkomst till vanliga kommandon.

trans-unit.source: You add a RibbonQuickAccessToolBar to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon> control by specifying it as the content of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property using XAML [Property Element Syntax](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du lägger till en RibbonQuickAccessToolBar till en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon>kontroll genom att ange den som innehållet i den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen med XAML [Egenskapselementsyntax](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon>

trans-unit.source: ``` <ribbon:Ribbon> <ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> <ribbon:RibbonQuickAccessToolBar /> </ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> ... </ribbon:Ribbon> ``` The following list shows the typical placement of the RibbonQuickAccessToolBar in the hierarchy of ribbon elements.
trans-unit.target: ``` <ribbon:Ribbon> <ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> <ribbon:RibbonQuickAccessToolBar /> </ribbon:Ribbon.QuickAccessToolBar> ... </ribbon:Ribbon> ```I följande lista visas vanliga placeringen av RibbonQuickAccessToolBar i hierarkin av element i menyfliksområdet.
